title: Index out of bounds

labels.name: I-ICE
labels.description: Issue: The compiler panicked, giving an Internal Compilation Error (ICE) ❄️

labels.name: T-compiler
labels.description: Relevant to the compiler team, which will review and decide on the PR/issue.

body:
`rustc` asked me to file this report.  I got the same error each time I tried to run `cargo check`.  Then I deleted `target/` and the error was gone.  

I cannot reproduce this issue.
